  "detailed_description": "Welcome to <strong>AMAYA’s LOST SOUL</strong>. In this 2d Action Game you play as Amaya the daughter of an all and mighty great <strong>“CREATOR”</strong>. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119380/extras/285b134bcdc729f638b7016c698ac8d0.poster.avif?t=1741391415\" width=660 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119380/extras/285b134bcdc729f638b7016c698ac8d0.webm?t=1741391415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119380/extras/285b134bcdc729f638b7016c698ac8d0.mp4?t=1741391415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>The great <strong>“CREATOR”</strong> is leader of the Out Raiders a cult who are looking to expand so to speak. You are tasked with taking down a kingdom under the command of the “CREATOR”. Will you follow through and commit to your masters will or fight back. Choices Matter in this 2d pixel art action game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119380/extras/9eec7f9b09d996d22952c37bb215ced7.poster.avif?t=1741391415\" width=660 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119380/extras/9eec7f9b09d996d22952c37bb215ced7.webm?t=1741391415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119380/extras/9eec7f9b09d996d22952c37bb215ced7.mp4?t=1741391415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>*Fluid 2d Combat System<br>*Boss Battles<br>* Multiple Endings<br>* Secrets spread across the land<br>*Meet a colorful cast of characters along the way<br>*Original Art brimming with personality<br>*Created mostly by one person<br>*Choices Matter in this Adventure<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119380/extras/2c86ea58deca0e0302ebce6631f60e2c.poster.avif?t=1741391415\" width=660 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119380/extras/2c86ea58deca0e0302ebce6631f60e2c.webm?t=1741391415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119380/extras/2c86ea58deca0e0302ebce6631f60e2c.mp4?t=1741391415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
